---
title: Vegan Turkish-Spiced Chickpea Bowls with Pistachio Basmati Rice & Lemon-Herb Hummus Sauce
description: A chickpea bowl is the epitome of plant-based perfection. In this one, Turkish-spiced chickpeas are roasted alongside onion wedges and grape tomatoes, then tossed with bright and tangy lemon zest. Veggies are served over a bed of fragrant basmati rice mixed with pistachios and golden raisins for texture and sweetness. And since the secret’s always in the sauce, you’ll finish things off with a drizzle of herby lemon hummus that brings all these flavors together. With so much to savor in one bowl, we guarantee any non-vegan dinner guests won’t even miss the meat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-turkish-spiced-chickpea-bowls-7e75f9ae.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/vegan-turkish-spiced-chickpea-bowls-62f2aa31d05d2b368a0a6fef-fe220b65.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/vegan-turkish-spiced-chickpea-bowls-62f2aa31d05d2b368a0a6fef
cuisine: Middle East
time required: 40 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 850 kcal
